{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·001.1", "text_original": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹猗猗，有匪君子，如切如磋，如琢如磨，瑟兮僩兮，赫兮咺兮，有匪君子，終不可諼兮。", "text_normalized": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹猗猗，有匪君子，如切如磋，如琢如磨，瑟兮僩兮，赫兮咺兮，有匪君子，終不可諼兮。", "notes": "淇奧 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·001.2", "text_original": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹青青，有匪君子，充耳琇瑩，會弁如星，瑟兮僩兮，赫兮咺兮，有匪君子，終不可諼兮。", "text_normalized": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹青青，有匪君子，充耳琇瑩，會弁如星，瑟兮僩兮，赫兮咺兮，有匪君子，終不可諼兮。", "notes": "淇奧 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-weifeng-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-weifeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·衛風·001.3", "text_original": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹如簀，有匪君子，如金如錫，如圭如璧，寬兮綽兮，倚重較兮，善戲謔兮，不為虐兮。", "text_normalized": "瞻彼淇奧，綠竹如簀，有匪君子，如金如錫，如圭如璧，寬兮綽兮，倚重較兮，善戲謔兮，不為虐兮。", "notes": "淇奧 Chinese stanza 3."}
